HEADWORD: Quater-cousin
<hw>Qua"ter-cous`in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>quatre</ets> four + <ets>cousin</ets>, E. <ets>cousin</ets>.]</ety>
<def>A cousin within the first four degrees of kindred.</def>⟦br⟧
